t=1726924872\" width=600 height=126 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156590/extras/4222077a2f64587e0af4fc6725ed6fbc.poster.avif?t=1726924872\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156590/extras/4222077a2f64587e0af4fc6725ed6fbc.webm?t=1726924872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156590/extras/4222077a2f64587e0af4fc6725ed6fbc.mp4?t=1726924872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Experience realistic weather, forecasted before each level that can change everyday.  You can even hunt at night if you’re brave enough!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156590/extras/38186d0a201bc238e02d18fd29d27bdd.avif?t=1726924872\" width=600 height=126 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156590/extras/76912c25bbcfab06e22d229a47be33df.poster.avif?t=1726924872\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156590/extras/76912c25bbcfab06e22d229a47be33df.webm?t=1726924872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156590/extras/76912c25bbcfab06e22d229a47be33df.mp4?t=1726924872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Features mythological creatures from real life stories of the forest like Bigfoot!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156590/extras/9be506ed613f664900ade92b688af883.avif?t=1726924872\" width=600 height=126 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156590/extras/7f3b081478a06bc5fa39541994b01fab.poster.avif?t=1726924872\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156590/extras/7f3b081478a06bc5fa39541994b01fab.webm?t=1726924872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156590/extras/7f3b081478a06bc5fa39541994b01fab.mp4?t=1726924872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Exploration Mode: Play as an animal! You will also be rewarded a point handicap! Unlock new animals and have fun exploring, although this mode does not count towards achievements or records.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A note from the developers:</h2>We are a small but very passionate team of brothers. We loved morel mushroom hunting growing up. We still do it every year. One of the greatest things about mushroom hunting is just being out in nature. We take a lot of photos while we are hunting which is how the game came about. We wanted to create an immersive experience of being out in nature, mushroom hunting, and photographing the beautiful environment around you into a game, without having to hunt something with a weapon.<br><br><br>Although one of the main goals of the game is to collect mushrooms, it Is Not a mushroom hunter simulator. Morels is an adventure game that focuses equally on mushroom hunting and photographing animals.<br><br>if you have any feedback, questions, or problems with the game please don't hesitate to contact us.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Other Notable Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore and discover new collectables like dinosaur bones.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 50 animals to discover and photograph. You can now even swim and photograph fish.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Enjoy a new experience each season you play. New mushroom locations, animal activity, weather, and more.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Take on weekly tasks including finding a certain number of mushrooms or photographing specific animals to get extra points. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 7 unique maps across the Unites States with exciting terrain and surprises! </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> View all your photos in your photo book. They are also saved to your PC to view anytime!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Learn tips and tricks inside your Hunter’s Manual to help you throughout the season. Unlock new pages by moving up in hunter levels!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Customize the game to your interests by choosing from a broad list of different music or just enjoy the calming sounds of nature.</li></ul>",
